    • Method Detail

      • wrapOutputArcExecutable

        public static de.renew.engine.searcher.Executable wrapOutputArcExecutable(de.renew.engine.searcher.Executable executable,
                                                                          RollbackArcExecutable rollbackArcExecutable)
        Wraps the executable in the SimpleOutputArcExecutable wrapper if the executable is output arc's executable, but not the rollback arc's executable. Otherwise, returns the given executable as is.
        Parameters:
        executable - The executable which is the candidate for wrapping.
        rollbackArcExecutable - The db-net transition's rollback arc's executable. May be null, if the transition has no rollback arcs.
        Returns:
        The wrapped executable if the executable is output arc's executable, but not the rollback arc's executable. Otherwise, returns the given executable as is.
